    • sendMessage

      public static boolean sendMessage(String sendMessage)
      Always try to execute the cached parsing of client message as a command. Requires that the execute field of the commands to be set to send to server so that they aren't treated as client command's that do nothing. Commands.performCommand(CommandSourceStack, String) for reference
      Parameters:
      sendMessage - the chat message
      Returns:
      false leaves the message to be sent to the server, true means it should be caught before LocalPlayer.chat(String)
